snippet.title: Piozila 2 - Gameplay 1-2
snippet.description:
Move a little chubby character to collect stars. Avoid traps and flee from humans, through several levels and chapters, in a very colorful and cute universe.

Available for free on Google Play and App Store.

Google Play : https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.menamenagames.piozila2
App Store : https://apps.apple.com/us/app/piozila-2/id6450461710

More information: menamenagames.com
